json","id":304302,"motion":100}],"textRight":"｜彩羽……你在生气吗？@为什么？｜"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":100101,"lipSynch":0,"motion":301}],"textLeft":"…………"},{"chara":[{"id":100101}],"textLeft":"我没生气。"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":100101,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"可我还是觉得使用暴力是不对的。"},{"chara":[{"id":100101}],"textLeft":"你能为我们着想，我很开心……"},{"chara":[{"id":100101}],"textLeft":"不过，不能遇事就用暴力解决。"},{"chara":[{"id":304302,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300}],"textRight":"｜…………｜"},{"chara":[{"id":100101,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"除了和魔女战斗、@特别危险的情况外，"},{"chara":[{"id":100101}],"textLeft":"我不希望你使用那个战斗形态。"},{"chara":[{"id":100101}],"textLeft":"我这么说也是为樱子你好……"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304302,"lipSynch":0}],"textRight":"｜…………｜"},{"chara":[{"id":100101,"motion":400}],"textLeft":"拜托你答应我，@不要随便使用那股力量。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":304302,"motion":0}],"textRight":"｜我知道了……我答应你。｜"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp.json","id":100101,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"太好了……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100101,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"谢谢你听我的话，@那我们就不说这个啦。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304302}],"textRight":"｜嗯。｜"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":304302},{"effect":"fadeout","id":100101}],"textClear":1},{"bgm":"bgm03_story02","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100301,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100501,"motion":100,"pos":1},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100401,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameCenter":"菲莉希亚","textCenter":"彩羽，我们来玩游戏吧！@我还叫忧来了！"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":100301},{"effect":"fadeout","id":100501},{"effect":"fadeout","id":100401}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100101,"motion":200,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304302,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"彩羽","textLeft":"看上去挺有趣的呢。@樱子也要玩吗？"},{"chara":[{"id":304302,"motion":30